<TABLE CLASS="SPELLS" WIDTH=100%>
<TR><TH>Notes on Charm<BR>
<I><FONT SIZE=-1>Posted 2000-01-17 20:01:56 by Daphandrea</FONT></I></TH></TR>
<TR><TD>     Charm is an excellent spell, of course only when used properly.<BR><BR>
Your target will, of course, attack you when charms wears off.<BR><BR>
Because of this, use charm for a quick disposable pet you'll only need once, because if you can quickly have it kill an enemy, get it injured, and the kill it off, you can save the tiny daggers on a pet and get sone decent exp.</TD></TR>
</TABLE>

